TunableList.name: BABY_PLACEMENT_TAGS
TunableList.description: When trying to place a baby bassinet on the lot, we attempt to place it near other objects on the lot. Those objects are determined in priority order by this tuned list. It will try to place next to all objects of the matching types, before trying to place the baby in the middle of the lot, and then finally trying the mailbox. If all FGL placements fail, we put the baby into the household inventory.
